# Copy the values you need into `.env.local` (git-ignored). This file documents the
# variables the app reads; never put real secrets here.
#
# Only variables prefixed with `VITE_` are exposed to client code (via `import.meta.env`).
# That prefix is a safety boundary, not a naming convention: anything you expose ends up
# in the bundle, readable by anyone. Secrets belong on a server, never here.
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000
